textBox.richText: Sadly our time with the Canadians had come to a close (it was evident that the weather was feeling our sadness as it still continues to bucket down constantly). We all had an awesome time together and are pumped that it will be less than 12 months until we next meet up. Californians are primed for Halloween with pumpkin and Halloween paraphernalia taking pride of place everywhere! Can’t wait to experience the festivities at the end of the trip.
